  • public class StorageDevice
extends DomainWrapper<com.abiquo.server.core.infrastructure.storage.StorageDeviceDto>
    Adds high level functionality to StorageDeviceDto. The Storage Device Resource offers the functionality of managing the external storage.

    Ignasi Barrera, Francesc Montserrat
